#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/polynomial/polynomial.py:docstring
#: of numpy.polynomial.polynomial.polyfromroots:31
msgid ""
"1-D array of the polynomial's coefficients If all the roots are real, then "
"`out` is also real, otherwise it is complex.  (see Examples below)."
msgstr ""

